author: bainbrid
body:
This PR contains a .root file containing weights for a BDT model used by the LowPtGsfElectronIDProducer module.

- The model is given the label "2020Nov28". 
- Important hyper-parameters: depth=13, trees=1000
- Training details: use 10_6_X UL samples from all 3 years of Run 2
- It replaces the "placeholder" 2020Sept15 model (from BParking studies).

https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/32391 depends in this PR.
title: LowPtElectrons: final ID model weights file
